RACE.FOOTNOTES: FRISSON set the pace in the three path, was roused in the two path around the turn, floated out to the five path turning into the lane, and was driven clear. COPANELLO BAY raced wellback in the three path, floated out to the six path and was coaxed early around the turn, fanned out to the nine path entering the stretch, and rallied for place. GABAGOOL prompted the pace in the four path, was driven between foes around the turn, but faded in the stretch. CORPORATE AFFAIR raced off the pace inside, was ridden in the two path into the turn, angled out to the eight path turning into the stretch, but made no impact. KOHAKU rated in the five path, was urged from the six path into the lane, but did not factor. STRAIGHT TIME trailed in the five path, was driven in the seven path around the turn, but never threatened. REAL ROCKET BOY bumped at the start with an inner foe, chased in the six path, was roused from the three path into the turn, but gaveway in upper stretch. CALLIHOO tracked in the two path but weakened entering the stretch.
